title: Average Number of Years Enrolled and Average Number of Years Elapsed between First Enrollment and Degree Completion, 2014–15 College Graduates

metadata.source: Doug Shapiro, Afet Dundar, Phoebe Khasiala Wakhungu, Xin Yuan, Angel Nathan, and Youngsik Hwang, Time to Degree: A National View of the Time Enrolled and Elapsed for Associate and Bachelor’s Degree Earners (Herndon, VA: National Student Clearinghouse Research Center, 2016).
